# This is the "Artistic Style" (astyle) configuration file used for the
# segmentation-fold project to format all the code files systematically.
# Details on this file can be found on the following website:
# <http://astyle.sourceforge.net/>

# After running cmake, you can run "make tidy" to let cmake
# automatically run astyle over all the code.

--add-brackets
--add-one-line-brackets
--align-pointer=name
#--align-reference=name

--fill-empty-lines
 
--indent=force-tab
--indent-cases
--indent-classes
--indent-col1-comments
--indent-switches														# case block is indented wrt switch

--lineend=linux
 
--pad-oper
--unpad-paren

#--style=break
--suffix=none															# no backups - we have subversion
